'''''Earth, Bear the Suffering of All''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[Back to Earth in Evernight]].

==Steps==
# Head to "Radiant Scarwood" Grove of Epiphany
# Talk with the mysterious Mountain Dweller
# Venture into the Grove, seek out Terravox
# Help Spirithief pass through this area
# Help Spirithief block the water outlet
# Help Spirithief modify the Prophecy Tablet
# Venture into the Grove, seek out Terravox
# Venture into the Grove, review the disordered memory
# Venture into the disordered memory and seek out Terravox
# Talk with Terravox, the Earth Demigod
# Talk with Hysilens
# Find (Trailblazer) and bring {{MC|f=her|m=him}} home.

